<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.7">
<l>pantaṇainta melviralāḷ cītaik kākip pakalavaṉmī tiyaṅkāta vilaṅkai vēntaṉ</l>
<l>antamiltiṇ karamciraṅkaḷ puraṇṭu vīḻa vaṭukaṇaiyā leytukanta vammāṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>centamiḻum vaṭakalaiyun tikaḻnta nāvar ticaimukaṉai yaṉaiyavarkaḷ cemmai mikka</l>
<l>vantaṇarta mākutiyiṉ pukaiyār celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who, for the sake of Sītā, the one with soft fingers like cotton,</l>
<l rend="indent">was happy having shot battle arrows</l>
<l>So the endless, strong arms and the heads fell, rolling from the king of Laṅkā,</l>
<l rend="indent">over which daylight never shines.</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr, filled with smoke from oblations</l>
<l>Of excellent priests of virtue, those who are like</l>
<l rend="indent">him who faces the directions, [and] those on whose tongues</l>
<l rend="indent">shine elegant Tamil and the northern language.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
